The paper deals with efficient algorithms for polynomial computations, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and algebraic algorithms (cs.SC). The use of arithmetic circuits and parameterized algorithms suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of data structures (cs.DS) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
